headline: Novavax Q3 Earnings & Sales Beat, Stock Falls 6% on '24 View Cut
summary: NVAX reports encouraging third-quarter results. However, the stock falls due to management lowering its sales guidance, citing lower COVID-19 vaccine uptake.
